<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph>This sample illustrates the conversion of Microsoft Excel document to PDF.</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>Essential XlsIO allows to export Excel document to PDF by using the Convert method of ExcelToPDFConverter class.	</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>   Supports conversion of Excel document to PDF document with cell values, cell styles, tables, charts, autoshapes, pictures, etc.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>  
